  "texts": [
    "MIMIC is a part of the MIMIC-III dataset.",
    "36 WikiGold 37 [69] is an annotated corpus including a small sample of Wikipedia articles in CoNLL format (IOB) [83].",
    "MUC-7 38 is a set of New York Times articles [33].",
    "CoNLL2003g 39 [152] was extracted from the German newspaper Frankfurter Rundshau, between September and December 1992.",
    "CoNLL2002 40 [153] is a collection of newswire articles from May 2000, made available by the Spanish EFE News Agency [153]."
